biography_text: MURPHY, Stephanie, a Representative from Florida; born in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam, September 16, 1978; B.A., College of William and Mary, Williamsburg, Va., 2000; M.S.F.S., Georgetown University, Washington, D.C., 2004; consultant; businesswoman; foreign affairs specialist, United States Department of Defense, 2004-2008; faculty, Rollins College, Winter Park, Fla., 2014-2016; elected as a Democrat to the One Hundred Fifteenth Congress (January 3, 2017-present).
